## Limitations

This report is based on available literature and online resources, which may not cover all aspects of the complex relationship between climate change and natural disasters. The findings are subject to the limitations of the sources used, including potential biases and the evolving nature of climate science. Further research and updated data are necessary to deepen the understanding of these impacts.